What you need to know:

EACC raised the red flag on Musila’s wealth on suspicion that he was a beneficiary of kickbacks from road contractors through an account at KCB Bank Kilifi branch.He denied the claims and rushed to court seeking to block the EACC investigation.Anti-Corruption Court judge Mumbi Ngugi has dismissed Musila’s petition, allowing EACC to investigate the source of his wealth.